{"tid":1013011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前頂級女模被渣夫拖累 散盡家產流落西班牙街頭","createTime":"2019-02-08T04:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T07:38:18.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b7cdedef39382402aaa5d3cce8e367ad0a607d","tid":1013011,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/08/99/5898325.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F08%2F99%2F5898325.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=aec24e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙名模曾經一年只需工作20日便可賺100萬美元。圖擷自Instagram<br />\n曾經是《Vogue》的封面人物，並且是YSL代言人的頂級模特兒，如今卻流落西班牙街頭。<br />\n根據《福斯新聞》報導，現年57歲的厄爾巴諾（Nastasia Urbano）20歲在巴賽隆納展開模特兒生涯。當時她不但是包括《Vogue》等國際知名雜誌的封面女郎，更是藝術大師安迪沃荷（Andy Warhol）、名導演波蘭斯基（Roman Polanski）等人的座上賓，常與梅拉尼格里菲思（Melanie Griffith）、唐強生（Don Johnson）等巨星們一起參加派對，甚至曾獲邀出席瑪丹娜與西恩潘的婚禮。<br />\n厄爾巴諾表示自己當時擁有一切，生活得像個女王。她說：「大家都喜歡我，一年工作只要20天就能賺進100萬美元（約3100萬新台幣），如此工作了三、四年。」<br />\n然而，這一切在遇到她前夫後，便完全變了調。在認識前夫後僅兩天，前夫便要求他買一台BMW，「而我就像個傻瓜，簽了支票。因為當時我墜入情網。」之後更是散盡家產，「除了背上的衣服外，什麼也沒留下。」她更表示與前夫的這段關係中，除了有孩子是唯一的「好事」，其餘都很恐怖。<br />\n如今，厄爾巴諾除了患有抑鬱症，更因無力負擔房租而接連被房東趕走。現在她在朋友的沙發和西班牙的銀行門廳之間交替著過夜。她說：「我希望我能盡快恢復，我希望我的孩子看到我過得好，這樣他們才能以我為榮。」<br />\n而厄爾巴諾的前同事們聽到她的消息也倍感震驚，紛紛伸出援手，希望幫助她重回工作。一位前模特賀瑞納（Hernando Herrera）說：「她可以帶給時尚界很多東西。她可以做很多事情，不僅是模特，還有會議，時尚演講和其他活動。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.heartyhosting.com/radaronline.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Vogue-Supermodel-Nastasia-Urbano-Broke-Homeless-PP.jpg?resize=540%2C400&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.heartyhosting.com%2Fradaronline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FVogue-Supermodel-Nastasia-Urbano-Broke-Homeless-PP.jpg%3Fresize%3D540%252C400%26ssl%3D1&h=c6b048c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3633614?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3633614%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catebreaknews_ch2&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1EBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=35a6b76b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3633614?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"d627247d4ca3cc5d7c6cbd7b6a4aeeb263aa4c55","tid":1013011,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3e42f153f6c64ad7081a1ed6ec80655b340eab","tid":1013011,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"冇自殺都算係咁"},{"pid":"c4cc2eb173b5677bdda3a063e6f78e2ec987498e","tid":1013011,"uid":110988,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺得美麗 居然係top model <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0712d59d93cd354850c641fb557f67cf89a0a34e","tid":1013011,"uid":60057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c4cc2eb173b5677bdda3a063e6f78e2ec987498e","tid":1013011,"uid":110988,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺得美麗 居然係top model <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"有時model唔係話要超靚既，D相都睇唔到佢身型。通常身型高挑加個樣有D COOL就係top model<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe7bae510e37e82ba2310fb27247ad6266a91ae","tid":1013011,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"所有男人都係鴨!"},{"pid":"38be975978b0956e48da0aaf8ae0f7d99b613e16","tid":1013011,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0712d59d93cd354850c641fb557